 the result</td>\n  </tr>\n  </table>\n<hr>\n\n<h2>Technical Details</h2>\n\n<table class=\"ws-table-all\">\n<tbody><tr>\n  <th style=\"width:25%\">Return Value:</th>\n  <td>The filename, as a String</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th>Node.js Version:</th>\n  <td>0.1.25</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<hr>\n<h2>More Examples</h2>\n<div class=\"w3-example\">\n<h3>Example</h3>\n  <p>Extract the filename, but not the \".js\" at the end:</p>\n<div class=\"w3-code notranslate jsHigh\">\n  var path = require(\'path\');<br><br>var filename = path.basename(\'/Users/Refsnes/demo_path.js\', \'.js\');<br>\n  console.log(filename);</div>\n  <a class=\"w3-btn w3-margin-bottom\" href=\"shownodejs_cmd.asp?filename=demo_met_path_basename2\" target=\"_blank\">Run example &raquo;</a>\n</div>\n<hr>\n\n<p>\n<a class=\"w3-btn w3-white w3-border\" href=\"ref_path.asp\">&#10094; Path Module</a>\n</p>\n<div id=\"mypagediv2\" style=\"position:relative;text-align:center;\"></div>\n<br>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"w3-col l2 m12\" id=\"right\">\n\n<div class=\"sidesection\">\n  <div id=\"skyscraper\">\n  \n    <div id=\"adngin-sidebar_top-0\"></div>\n  \n  </div>\n</div>\n  \n<style>\n.ribbon-vid {\n  font-size:12px;\n  font-weight:bold;\n  padding: 6px 20px;\n  left:-20px;\n  top:-10px;\n  text-align: center;\n  color:black;\n  border-radius:25px;\n}\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"sidesection\" id=\"video_sidesection\">\n  <div class=\"w3-center\" style=\"padding-bottom:7px\">\n    <span class=\"ribbon-vid ws-yellow\">NEW</span>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.5;font-family: Source Sans Pro;padding-left:4px;padding-right:4px;\">We just launched<br>W3Schools videos</p>\n  <a onclick=\"ga(\'send\', \'event\', \'Videos\' , \'fromSidebar\');\" href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/videos/index.php\" class=\"w3-hover-opacity\"><img src=\"/images/htmlvideoad_footer.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;padding:5px 10px 25px 10px\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>\n  <a class=\"ws-button\" style=\"font-size:16px;text-dec